title: Serbia rebukes Croatia minister for calling Vučić a Russian ‘satellite’

title: Netanyahu says no deal yet on Gaza cease-fire, remains bullish on Rafah operation
description: “You can’t have victory until you eliminate Hamas,” Netanyahu said, adding that likely expanded operations in the southern Gaza city of Rafah are “weeks, not months” away from completion.

title: Navalny’s death a sign of Putin’s weakness, US national security adviser says
description: The “idea that he had to lock this guy up, try to muzzle and silence him, and now he’s trying to suppress and silence anyone who wants to come out and mourn him — that’s a sign of weakness,” U.S. national security adviser said.

title: 10 ways a second Trump term could be more extreme than the first
description: From nationwide abortion bans to classroom culture wars, assaults on climate science and political weaponization of the military, his return to the White House could make Trump 1.0 seem tame.

title: Trump scores easy knockout of Nikki Haley in South Carolina
description: The former president’s win — which was so decisive that the AP projected him the victor solely based on a voter survey — came in the home state of his only major Republican rival, Nikki Haley.
